  "subject": "Improved error handling and reporting.",
  "commit_message": "Improved error handling and reporting.\n\nDG workflow does not stop when a error is returned from a node template execution\nThis patch changes the default success status into a failure if any error\nwere populated in the Blueprint errors collection.\nIt also prevents any error happening during the output resolution of an\nincomplete workflow from replacing the previously populated failure status\nand message, thereby hiding the real source of the error.\n\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-1942\n\nSigned-off-by: Serge Simard <serge@agilitae.com>\nChange-Id: Iff1d9a1ade8deffcf5b1d8876e89cb19f038a3e4\nSigned-off-by: Serge Simard <serge@agilitae.com>\n",
